      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hi, I'm a member of a local school board and we're currently working on updating our district's guidelines. Could you help me draft a formal policy regarding the use of personal cell phones in classrooms? We need to find a balance between allowing students to have them for safety/contacting parents and minimizing constant distractions during instructional time. Please include sections for Permitted Use, Prohibited Use, and Consequences.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
